[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    346[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    347[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **L6. Time-zone handling of snapshot and forecast timestamps not architecturally specified.** (Voice, Finding V3) **Fix:** Specify UTC-instant storage for `snapshot_ts`, `generated_at_ts`, and `forecast_for_ts`; DynamoDB serving record carries both UTC and hospital-local with explicit offset and DST flag; EventBridge cron on UTC, not local; first-cycle-after-DST-transition skip rule.
